data.description: Beautiful  2 story home in Whitehall Subdivision -This home is situated in a cul-de-sac where you can enjoy watching nature gather at the pond across the street. As you enter into the home, step into the living room where  you can have family night or entertain your guest in the formal dining room.  Venture to the kitchen and have great conversations as you prepare the days meal. The kitchen has laundry room and 2 pantry areas with a half bath for your convenience. This home features 4 bedroom and 2 1/2 bath, the refrigerator, range and dishwasher remain with the property.  Home had new roof installed with new gutters and downspouts in 2023 by Power Home Remodeling and has a transferable warranty for the new buyer, Hot water heater replaced in 10/2022 by Morris Jenkins, Air conditioning replaced by Morris Jenkins on 6/2017, Heating unit was replaced by Morris Jenkins on 1/2022. Palmetto Exterminating holds termite bond on home since purchase in 2005 . Don't miss out - A Rare Find!
